---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		
		<title>Welcome to Everdantia - Everdantia Blog</title>
		<meta name="description" content="Discover the magical world where digital nature meets real conservation efforts. Step into a realm where every pixel tells a story of growth, wonder, and environmental hope." />
		
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
		
		<style>
			* {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			body {
				font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
				background: #f8f6f2;
				color: #4d6b3c;
				line-height: 1.6;
			}

			.hero {
				position: relative;
				height: 60vh;
				min-height: 500px;
				color: white;
				overflow: hidden;
			}

			.hero-image {
				position: absolute;
				inset: 0;
				z-index: -2;
			}

			.hero-image img {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				object-fit: cover;
			}

			.hero-overlay {
				position: absolute;
				inset: 0;
				background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4), rgba(0,0,0,0.2), rgba(0,0,0,0.4));
				z-index: -1;
			}

			.hero-content {
				position: relative;
				height: 100%;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				justify-content: center;
				padding: 2rem;
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				text-align: center;
			}

			.nav-back {
				position: absolute;
				top: 2rem;
				left: 2rem;
				color: white;
				text-decoration: none;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.5rem;
				font-weight: 500;
				background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
				padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 2rem;
				backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
				transition: all 0.3s ease;
				background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
				padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 2rem;
				backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
			}

			.nav-back:hover {
				background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
				transform: translateX(-5px);
			}

			.article-meta {
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				gap: 1rem;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
			}

			.category-tag {
				background: rgba(139,171,93,0.9);
				color: white;
				padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
				border-radius: 1.5rem;
				font-size: 0.8rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.05em;
			}

			.hero-section h1 {
				font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
				font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
				font-weight: 700;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
				text-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
				line-height: 1.1;
			}

			.container {
				max-width: 900px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 0 2rem;
				position: relative;
				z-index: 1;
			}

			.article {
				background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
				border-radius: 2rem;
				margin: -4rem auto 4rem;
				position: relative;
				z-index: 1;
				box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
				overflow: hidden;
				backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
				border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
			}

			.featured-image {
				width: 100%;
				height: 400px;
				object-fit: cover;
			}

			.article-content {
				padding: 4rem;
			}

			.article-content .content {
				font-size: 1.15rem;
				line-height: 1.8;
				color: #4d6b3c;
			}

			.article-content .content p {
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}

			.article-content .content h2 {
				font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
				font-size: 2rem;
				color: #6b4f2a;
				margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem;
				position: relative;
			}

			.article-content .content h2::before {
				content: '';
				position: absolute;
				left: -2rem;
				top: 50%;
				transform: translateY(-50%);
				width: 0.25rem;
				height: 2rem;
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8bab5d, #6b4f2a);
				border-radius: 0.125rem;
			}

			.article-content .content p:first-of-type {
				font-size: 1.25rem;
				color: #6b4f2a;
				font-weight: 500;
			}

			.article-content .content p:first-of-type::first-letter {
				font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
				font-size: 4rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				float: left;
				line-height: 1;
				margin: 0.1rem 0.5rem 0 0;
				color: #8bab5d;
			}

			.sharing-section {
				background: rgba(139,171,93,0.1);
				padding: 2rem;
				margin: 3rem -4rem -4rem;
				border-radius: 0 0 2rem 2rem;
				text-align: center;
				backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
			}

			.sharing-section h3 {
				font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
				color: #6b4f2a;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.share-buttons {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
				gap: 1rem;
			}

			.share-btn {
				display: inline-flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.5rem;
				padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
				background: #8bab5d;
				color: white;
				text-decoration: none;
				border-radius: 2rem;
				font-weight: 500;
				transition: all 0.3s ease;
			}

			.share-btn:hover {
				background: #6b4f2a;
				transform: translateY(-2px);
			}

			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				.hero-section {
					padding: 6rem 1rem 4rem;
				}
				
				.article-content {
					padding: 2rem;
				}
				
				.sharing-section {
					margin: 2rem -2rem -2rem;
				}
				
				.nav-back {
					top: 1rem;
					left: 1rem;
					padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
				}
				
				.share-buttons {
					flex-direction: column;
					align-items: center;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<section class="hero-section">
			<a href="/blog" class="nav-back">
				‚Üê Back to Blog
			</a>
			
			<div class="hero-content">
				<div class="article-meta">
					<span class="category-tag">Community</span>
					<span>‚Ä¢</span>
					<span>January 15, 2025</span>
					<span>‚Ä¢</span>
					<span>3 min read</span>
				</div>
				<h1>Welcome to Everdantia</h1>
			</div>
		</section>

		<div class="container">
			<article class="article">
				<img src="/images/environment/everdantia-glade/glade0.jpg" 
					 alt="Everdantia Glade" 
					 class="featured-image" />
				
				<div class="article-content">
					<div class="content">
						<p>Welcome to Everdantia, where each NFT represents more than just digital art‚Äîit's a gateway to a living, breathing world where imagination meets purpose.</p>
						
						<p>In our enchanted realm, every tree tells a story. From the ancient Elder Oak that holds the memories of countless generations to the shimmering Crystal Birch that reflects the magic flowing through our forest, each creation is born from a vision of harmony between the digital and natural worlds.</p>
						
						<h2>A New Kind of NFT Project</h2>
						
						<p>Everdantia isn't just another collection of digital art pieces. We're building a community-driven narrative where your participation shapes the story. As an NFT holder, you become part of our ever-expanding lore, with opportunities to influence seasonal events, vote on new additions, and help write the future chapters of our enchanted forest.</p>
						
						<p>But our mission extends beyond the digital realm. Each purchase supports real-world conservation efforts, making your investment in digital nature a contribution to protecting actual forests. This is where blockchain technology meets environmental responsibility.</p>
						
						<h2>The Journey Begins</h2>
						
						<p>Our Genesis Collection of 100 unique trees represents the foundation of Everdantia. These aren't randomly generated images‚Äîeach tree is carefully crafted with its own personality, backstory, and role in our growing mythology.</p>
						
						<p>As we prepare for our August 1st mint, we invite you to explore our world, join our community, and become part of something truly special. This is just the beginning of what promises to be an extraordinary journey through the digital wilderness.</p>
						
						<p>Welcome to Everdantia. Welcome home.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="sharing-section">
						<h3>Share this story</h3>
						<div class="share-buttons">
							<a href={`https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=${encodeURIComponent('Just read "Welcome to Everdantia" - Discover a magical world where digital nature protects the real one! üåø‚ú®')}&url=${encodeURIComponent('https://everdantia.art/blog/welcome-to-everdantia')}`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="share-btn">
								üê¶ Share on Twitter
							</a>
							<a href="https://discord.gg/enqAsyDU" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="share-btn">
								üí¨ Join Discord
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</article>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>